Class LoginScreen
    Initialize state

    Function build (Building the UI)
        Display Email and Password input fields
        Display "Login" button

        IF user clicks "Login" THEN
            Check if email and password are valid
            IF email and password are valid THEN
                Authenticate user with Firebase
                IF authentication is successful THEN
                    Navigate to SelectScreen
                ELSE
                    Display error message
                ENDIF
            ELSE
                Display validation error message
            ENDIF
        ENDIF

        IF user clicks "Forgot Password" THEN
            Navigate to ForgotPasswordScreen
        ENDIF

        IF user clicks "Back" THEN
            Navigate to HomeScreen
        ENDIF
End Class

Start
|
Display Email and Password input fields
|
Did user enter email and password?
|     
Yes --> Are email and password valid? --> Yes --> Authenticate with Firebase --> Success? --> Yes --> Navigate to SelectScreen --> End
|      |
|      No                                                   No
|      |                                                    |
|      Display validation error message                      Display error message
|
No
|
Display "Forgot Password" link
|
Did user click "Forgot Password"? --> Yes --> Navigate to ForgotPasswordScreen --> End
|
No
|
Display "Back" button
|
Did user click "Back"? --> Yes --> Navigate to HomeScreen --> End
|
End
